nce" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01405">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 9. 6. 1904</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01407">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, [19.? 6. 1904]</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01403">Schnitzler, Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 22. 5. 1904</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01407">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, [19.? 6. 1904]</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
